data.description: This stunning two-story townhouse features 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, spacious living and family rooms with access to a one car garage, a modern kitchen with wood-finish cabinetry and stainless steel appliances, and a generous dining area. Enjoy the brick-floored screened patio and fully fenced backyard for relaxation and privacy. The luxurious master bedroom upstairs boasts a spacious walk-in closet and an elegant master bathroom with dual sinks and a glass shower. Community offers a beautiful resort style clubhouse with Olympic sized pool, water park, fitness center and more. Conveniently located next to major retail destinations, Turnpike, and Homestead Baptist Hospital. Minutes away from the Florida Keys. Low HOA!!! Enjoy immersive 3D virtual tour. May the Force be with you!
